Duty free import of specified goods 



Duty free import of Pharmaceutical reference standards



Accelerated depreciation allowance for investment on plant and machinery



Support in the form of loans/grants for industrial R&D 



Financial support to meet the developmental expenditure for R&D 


 
 


 

Rajgopal R&D Consultancy Pvt. Ltd. deals with the product/process development activity of specialty chemicals, pharma intermediates and API’s. 




