"Quality and Care that's what I believe in; Every garment manufactured by Rajgopal reflects just that" ~ Gopal Chandak, Managing Director - Rajgopal

Incorporated in the year 2000, Rajgopal is one of the quality Indian manufacturers and exporters of Shirting Fabrics, Suiting Fabrics, Uniform Fabrics, Garments, Upholstery Fabrics etc. We have our own manufacturing unit which uses state-of-the-art technology to provide our clients with quality products at competitive prices. Read More













Shirting Fabrics

 We manufacture a wide range of quality shirting fabrics including Cotton, Polyester and  Blended Fabrics in a wide amalgamation of colours.  
